OL,7,FA man who was fined for not paying to
OL,8,Fuse the Dartford Crossing despite
OL,9,Fhaving an account has covered his
OL,10,Fentire living room floor with over 100
OL,11,Fpenalty letters.
OL,13,FPaul Kelly from Essex says he's
OL,14,Freceived 151 Dart Charge fines in
OL,15,Ftotal.
OL,17,FThe crossing was part of his daily
OL,18,Fcommute from Rayleigh to Kent nearly
OL,19,Fevery day last year while he worked as
OL,20,Fa DJ.
