OL,7,FDespite having a registered account,
OL,8,Fhis vehicle was triggering fines for
OL,9,Fnot paying the fee incurred when using
OL,10,Fthe connection between Essex and Kent.
OL,12,FHe says he has been in communication
OL,13,Fwith National Highways but is worried
OL,14,Fabout the fines looming over him.
OL,16,FPaul renewed his account when he was
OL,17,Ftold to last July, however he started
OL,18,Fgetting daily fines in January 2024.
