OL,7,FSince then, he has appealed the fines
OL,8,Fand was eventually told to just pay
OL,9,Fthe fees.
OL,11,FHe says the stress he was under for
OL,12,Fthree months was 'unbearable' as the
OL,13,Ffines would have cost him around
OL,14,F#5,000, or #10,000 if he didn't pay
OL,15,Fstraight away.
