OL,7,FPaul isn't alone. Terri Wilson and her
OL,8,Fhusband have told ITV News Meridian
OL,9,Fthey have pre-paid accounts, but have
OL,10,Fbeen fined 12 times. She has been told
OL,11,Fby Dart Charge she will get the money
OL,12,Fback for eight of those fines.
OL,14,FA National Highways spokesperson said:
OL,15,F"In November, Mr Kelly was given the
OL,16,Fopportunity to settle all his
OL,17,Foutstanding crossings at the normal
OL,18,Fcrossing rate for his account.
