OL,7,F"If customers have received fines that
OL,8,Fthey feel are incorrect there is a
OL,9,Fchallenge process available. If the
OL,10,Foutcome of the customers challenge is
OL,11,Fsuccessful they will be refunded,
OL,12,Fhowever road user charges may still be
OL,13,Fpayable."
OL,15,FDart Charge was designed to speed up
OL,16,Fjourney times at one of the UK's
OL,17,Fbusiest transport gateways, getting
OL,18,Frid of physical terminals so drivers
OL,19,Fcan use the crossing without having to
OL,20,Fpay the charge at a barrier.
