OL,7,FDrivers using the Dartford Crossing
OL,8,Fhave to pay the Dart Charge in advance
OL,9,For by midnight the day after crossing.
OL,10,FPeople can pay online or by phone,
OL,11,Fpost or at retail outlets. It is free
OL,12,Fto use the crossing from 22:00 to
OL,13,F06:00.
OL,15,FOn the official government website it
OL,16,Fsays: "You can get a #70 fine if you
OL,17,Fdo not pay the Dart Charge.
OL,19,F"You must pay the fine within 28 days
OL,20,Fof receiving a Penalty Charge Notice
OL,21,F(PCN).
